{"tid":2108098,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港自救系列 同學們請廣傳】保安局已發出超過20萬張豁免強制檢疫","createTime":"2020-07-14T10:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T11:21:22.000Z","uid":259088,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"089392f58aa1d83afcdbada9524d9f63963a06e5","tid":2108098,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&amp;d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&amp;h=db2ec383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.rthk.hk%252Frthk%252Fch%252Fcomponent%252Fk2%252F1536645-20200708.htm%26d%3DgCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%253D%26h%3Ddb2ec383&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuIvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=59fbfb92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&amp;d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&amp;h=db2ec383</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">今年2月至5月在各出入境管制站，向獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，發出超過20萬張醫學監察通知書。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜關注，自抵港人士必須接受強制檢疫14天的規例實施以來，每月有多少來自內地、澳門及台灣的人士，獲豁免遵守有關規定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">保安局書面答覆</span></span></strong>指出，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">今年2月共發出93602張醫學監察通知書、3月發出39211張、4月發出36039張，5月發出40220張。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，根據規例，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，在留港期間要進行14天醫學監察，須戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次，如有不適應向衞生署呈報。</span></span></strong>有關人士在入境時，均須通過衞生署在口岸進行的體溫監測和健康申報程序。<br />\n_________________________________________<br />\n保安局仲係等到有議員主動去查詢，先至有<strong>書面回覆</strong>啊！！！<br />\n6月7月個數據黑洞仲未公佈出嚟啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同學們，我唔係想請你哋入嚟望兩下比個like同dislike或者推下post就算數，係想請你哋加入一齊行動！！用你哋嘅方式將真實情況宣傳開去！！<br />\n香港需要我哋自己救！！<